(1365, 1, '2021-04-24 03:37:28', '2021-04-24 03:37:28', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p id=\"yui_3_17_2_1_1618457139304_309\">We think it goes without saying that a great deal has happened since our last update. In what felt like a matter of days, the COVID-19 virus evolved from an illness few people had heard of into a large-scale global pandemic. Like you, we are in a state of shock and disbelief. Our hearts go out to those who have been impacted by this virus and our hard-working medical workers on the front lines.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In our respective home countries, the EZ365 team and our advisory network are experiencing the effects of the pandemic and witnessing the shocking impact it is having on the global economy. Our families are keeping up with the latest news from the safety of our homes and hope that you and your family are also placing a priority on staying healthy and safe.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As you know, our plan was to launch our digital asset exchange, EZ Exchange, in Q1 of 2020. Despite the platform being ready to go, after careful consideration, we have decided to delay our launch until a more suitable time. This was certainly a difficult decision for our team, however, we are sure you can appreciate that it is the most appropriate course of action given the current situation.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In terms of the EZ365 token, we will continue with our original plan of launching the EZ365 token with a later version of EZ Exchange  thus protecting the value of our token for both investors and token holders.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We will share more information about the launch of our token when more details are available.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As always, we appreciate your ongoing support of EZ365. While it has been one heck of a journey, we are as confident as ever in our offering and when we launch we will bring unique value to the digital asset space. Stay safe and be well!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Update: March 20', 'We think it goes without saying that a great deal has happened since our last update...', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '146-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-04-24 03:37:28', '2021-04-24 03:37:28', '', 146, 'https://ez365.io/?p=1365', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
