(1368, 1, '2021-04-28 22:41:10', '2021-04-28 22:41:10', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>On behalf of the entire EZ365 Team, we are pleased to announce that EZ Exchange OU (EZ Exchange), the Estonian corporation that owns EZ365 and all of its affiliated entities (EZWin, EZAcademy, EZNFT, etc) has been acquired by WEE-CIG International Corp, a publicly traded Nevada corporation, which has its shares listed on OTCMarkets: PINK under the ticker, WCIG.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This strategic acquisition is expected to provide the Company with operational capital, allowing us to realize our vision of building EZ365 into the premier, blockchain-based ecosystem on the web. EZ365 has been developed to become a primary destination for anyone interested in all forms of digital assets - from traditional cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin and Ethereum, to NFT art and&nbsp;metaverse property, to gaming and eSports.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We expect both WCIG and EZ Exchange to provide additional information for shareholders and investors in the coming weeks to clarify the direction of the companies, and our native EZ365 token. Please stay tuned and thank you for joining us on this amazing EZ journey!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Update April 2021', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'update-april-2021', '', '', '2021-06-30 01:28:42', '2021-06-30 01:28:42', '', 0, 'https://ez365.io/?p=1368', 0, 'post', '', 0),
