(1390, 3, '2021-06-30 03:54:25', '2021-06-30 03:54:25', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The&nbsp;excitement at EZ365&nbsp;continues as we&nbsp;ramp&nbsp;up&nbsp;our EZ NFT business!&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Offering&nbsp;new and expert traders an opportunity to participate in the&nbsp;non-fungible tokens (NFT)&nbsp;space in a number of revolutionary ways, EZ NFT serves as an easy on-ramp to the digital renaissance.&nbsp;Thats because, like all EZ365 offerings, were focused on providing a simple, efficient and&nbsp;incredible user experience that enables&nbsp;<em>everyone</em>&nbsp;to participate  from new entrants to experts.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Users&nbsp;can&nbsp;quickly and easily&nbsp;learn and trade their way to an NFT&nbsp;portfolio:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Buying&nbsp;Ethereum&nbsp;via credit card on EZ Exchange so they can begin to invest in the NFT market;&nbsp;</li><li>Buying and trading a variety of NFT tokens&nbsp;(coming soon);&nbsp;</li><li>Leveraging EZ Academy to better understand and&nbsp;navigate the world of NFTs&nbsp;(coming soon); and,&nbsp;</li><li>Participating in one of many&nbsp;upcoming&nbsp;opportunities to acquire NFT assets at auction.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Auctions will be held by&nbsp;Renaissance 2.0 &nbsp;a new division of EZ NFT&nbsp;that&nbsp;offers&nbsp;once&nbsp;in a lifetime opportunities to acquire iconic physical art along with uniquely commissioned, one-of-a-kind NFTs.&nbsp;This is a highly unique offering in the NFT (and art) space and bridges the current gap between digital and physical art.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Renaissance 2.0</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our first&nbsp;Renaissance 2.0&nbsp;auction will take place&nbsp;July 10<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;at 10pm&nb